Yeah I'm aware the intro, including the rest of the video drags on way more than necessary. But I guess thats just good ole' Darth for ya. 

I suppose it's more like a slow burn.. as if someone trying to drag a cigarette in middle of winter as the cold wind & snow blows, and the tiny ember glowing red has nearly died out. Fortunately, this is a YT video & not a cancer stick. So hopefully you can manage it. 

And again...No. I obviously I don't actually want Amber dead nor do I wish any harm upon her (except financially of course lol) 

I hope those who are offended will unsubscribe. because it only gets edgier from here 😅🥴
